&lt;li&gt;2-year Associates degree or equivalent experience is desired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proper phone etiquette and effective listening skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to speak and write clearly and accurately with demonstrated proficiency in typing and grammar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of customer service principles and practices (ITIL training a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
